     <td width="114" align="center" valign="top"> <p><a href="http://www.sociology.ucr.edu"><img src="images/smimage.gif" width="93" height="94" alt="Sociology Department" border="0"></a></p> <p><a href="http://www.sociology.ucr.edu"><img src="images/dept.gif" width="105" height="75" border="0"></a></p> <p><font size="3"><a href="http://www.ucr.edu"><img src="images/ucrhome.gif" alt="UCR" width="100" height="94" border="0"></a></font></p> <p>&nbsp;</p> </td> 
